data.description: This charming property can be found on a secluded hilltop with a private road and walking trails, offering peace and privacy. Situated on a wooded 3-acre lot, the property features a beautiful 1745 sq ft one-level home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a flex room that could serve as a 4th bedroom, a spacious living room, & eat-in kitchen. NO Carpet, Laminate, Tile and True Hardwood Floors Throughout. Huge 2-Tiered Back Deck is perfect for relaxing and enjoying the serene surroundings, sitting by the campfire, and watching the abundance of wildlife. Only 15 Min from Clarksville / Fort Campbell. Between the woods, the secluded lot, and the privacy of not being seen from the road, this is truly a rustic paradise and won’t last long! Recently renovated Kitchen with newer Double Ovens, Newer Dishwasher and 6 Burner Cooktop. Newer modern light fixtures. Newer Heat Pump. Roof (2021) with 30-year architectural shingles. Septic Pumped (2021). HVAC Regularly Serviced.
